WEBVTT

00:13.000 --> 00:14.430
Due to the absence

00:14.480 --> 00:16.280
of a father figure in his birth family,

00:16.280 --> 00:18.210
the killer developed
deep-seated inferiority

00:18.210 --> 00:19.940
and an extreme craving for love

00:20.120 --> 00:20.980
and attention.

00:21.550 --> 00:22.610
I also believe that

00:23.030 --> 00:25.230
he was abandoned by his mother
at some point.

00:25.230 --> 00:26.760
How is it? Handsome, right?

00:27.840 --> 00:29.570
Where did you get these videos?

00:30.660 --> 00:31.660
Didn't you tell me

00:31.710 --> 00:32.670
about Professor Jiang's

00:32.670 --> 00:33.350
prime-time

00:33.370 --> 00:34.760
legal program interview?

00:34.760 --> 00:35.490
So I found it.

00:35.500 --> 00:37.490
I searched too. How come I didn't find it?

00:37.490 --> 00:39.430
How could you possibly find it online?

00:39.430 --> 00:41.030
I asked the TV station for it.

00:41.390 --> 00:42.720
I made a copy of it. Here.

00:43.140 --> 00:45.030
Historical records of
the National Little Rose.

00:45.030 --> 00:45.790
What the heck?

00:45.790 --> 00:47.390
Na-National Little Rose?

00:47.870 --> 00:49.390
At that time, the TV station

00:49.390 --> 00:50.780
didn't know Professor Jiang's name,

00:50.780 --> 00:51.790
but they were deeply impressed by him

00:51.790 --> 00:53.470
and his red suit.

00:53.470 --> 00:54.710
So they gave him this nickname,

00:54.710 --> 00:56.640
and it stuck around.

00:58.260 --> 01:00.060
National Little Rose.

01:00.710 --> 01:01.520
But now

01:01.540 --> 01:03.690
he's been privatized by you.

02:32.500 --> 02:38.040
[Sunsets Secrets Regrets]

02:38.390 --> 02:40.900
[Episode 15]

02:41.620 --> 02:42.340
Mr. Wang.

02:48.750 --> 02:50.010
Hit a snag, didn't you?

02:50.630 --> 02:52.230
I told you not to come today,

02:52.280 --> 02:53.680
but you wouldn't listen.

02:54.079 --> 02:55.960
You might be a godsend elsewhere,

02:55.960 --> 02:56.960
but here,

02:57.560 --> 02:59.120
you're a total jinx.

02:59.120 --> 03:00.310
Don't you know that?

03:00.520 --> 03:01.840
And why on earth is that?

03:01.840 --> 03:02.470
Ask him.

03:03.590 --> 03:05.190
The case was already solved back then.

03:05.190 --> 03:06.590
It was my appeal material

03:06.650 --> 03:08.910
handed directly to
the provincial procuratorate

03:08.910 --> 03:10.570
that made them take a big fall.

03:11.790 --> 03:13.390
You can't be blamed for that.

03:18.240 --> 03:19.700
Are you done with your PDA?

03:20.340 --> 03:22.200
If so, let's get down to business.

03:22.900 --> 03:23.329
Alright,

03:23.329 --> 03:24.970
don't count on them for this.

03:26.050 --> 03:27.280
About what you told me last time—
that you suspected

03:27.280 --> 03:28.710
Qi Yan might be a twin—

03:29.460 --> 03:31.260
I've actually found some clues.

03:32.300 --> 03:33.340
Want to hear them?

03:36.530 --> 03:37.590
It's been 20 years.

03:38.450 --> 03:40.530
I'm already retired,

03:40.920 --> 03:42.550
and you still come to bother me.

03:42.550 --> 03:43.960
That's a bit too much, Director.

03:43.960 --> 03:45.360
What do you mean by bothering you?

03:45.360 --> 03:47.320
I'm just asking you to recall something.

03:47.320 --> 03:48.970
You coming back to ask me

03:50.170 --> 03:51.450
means this case

03:51.630 --> 03:52.840
has hit a dead end, right?

03:52.840 --> 03:54.030
What do you mean by hitting a dead end?

03:54.030 --> 03:55.079
Isn't this a new clue right here?

03:55.079 --> 03:56.010
Take a good look.

03:57.250 --> 03:57.730
Look.

04:03.560 --> 04:04.630
"The perpetrator

04:05.080 --> 04:08.030
has serious cognitive bias against women.

04:09.050 --> 04:10.580
Single-parent family..."

04:12.660 --> 04:14.060
Alright, that's enough.

04:14.920 --> 04:15.720
Let me ask you,

04:15.870 --> 04:18.670
you've been in the Xiacheng District
for decades.

04:19.630 --> 04:21.360
Has there been a family

04:21.480 --> 04:23.970
with a woman raising a child

04:24.730 --> 04:26.530
but unable to support the child?

04:26.870 --> 04:28.110
Think carefully.

04:31.480 --> 04:32.610
I need time to think.

04:39.190 --> 04:41.050
Do you remember the first victim?

04:42.159 --> 04:42.830
Yes, I do.

04:43.320 --> 04:44.960
Going back a few years,

04:45.390 --> 04:47.470
when we were visiting that area,

04:48.360 --> 04:51.090
we checked the whole neighborhood
around there—

04:51.270 --> 04:52.330
every corner of it.

04:52.950 --> 04:53.950
And you know what?

04:54.750 --> 04:56.720
One of the households told me

04:57.390 --> 04:58.510
that their house

04:58.510 --> 04:59.950
was for rent,

05:00.270 --> 05:01.430
and they once

05:01.920 --> 05:03.070
rented it to a woman.

05:03.480 --> 05:04.800
That woman was exceptionally beautiful,

05:04.800 --> 05:06.860
so they remembered her very clearly.

05:07.040 --> 05:07.870
They told me

05:07.870 --> 05:08.830
that that woman

05:09.070 --> 05:09.870
had no job

05:09.950 --> 05:11.080
and rarely went out.

05:11.310 --> 05:13.570
But different men kept coming to see her.

05:14.230 --> 05:15.080
Prostitution?

05:15.080 --> 05:16.810
We couldn't be sure about that.

05:18.360 --> 05:19.960
I remember 2 of her neighbors

05:20.390 --> 05:22.070
kept gossiping to me,

05:22.190 --> 05:23.250
saying things like

05:23.390 --> 05:24.430
that family

05:24.430 --> 05:25.920
took in an unclean woman

05:26.310 --> 05:28.190
who earned dirty money.

05:29.360 --> 05:30.360
Did she have a son?

05:30.680 --> 05:31.360
Yes.

05:31.560 --> 05:32.930
Two sons, twins.

05:33.700 --> 05:35.300
Did you look into that woman?

05:38.700 --> 05:40.159
You must be hungry, right?

05:41.230 --> 05:43.760
After the vice squad got the report
back then,

05:44.390 --> 05:45.450
they went to check,

05:45.740 --> 05:48.470
only to find she had moved out
early that morning.

05:48.830 --> 05:50.870
Besides knowing she was pretty,

05:51.490 --> 05:53.490
they didn't even have a photo of her.

05:53.870 --> 05:54.680
Plus,

05:54.830 --> 05:56.540
the landlord hadn't signed

05:56.560 --> 05:58.320
a formal lease with her,

05:59.070 --> 06:01.130
so there was no further information.

06:01.600 --> 06:03.800
Even the fact that she had twin sons

06:04.220 --> 06:05.290
was only discovered by the landlord

06:05.290 --> 06:06.170
by accident.

06:06.870 --> 06:07.800
At that time, the landlord

06:07.800 --> 06:09.310
told me a story.

06:09.870 --> 06:10.920
He said one day

06:11.390 --> 06:12.750
he went to read the water meter,

06:12.750 --> 06:13.810
and no one was home.

06:14.040 --> 06:15.630
He saw on the living room table

06:15.630 --> 06:16.600
a photo.

06:17.310 --> 06:19.510
Since the woman was very pretty,

06:19.990 --> 06:21.850
he took a closer look at the photo.

06:22.190 --> 06:22.800
He said

06:23.120 --> 06:25.520
it was a photo of that woman
and her two sons.

06:25.800 --> 06:28.070
The two sons looked exactly the same.

06:31.230 --> 06:32.200
So that means

06:32.380 --> 06:33.550
he only saw the photo

06:33.570 --> 06:36.170
and never actually met the children
in person?

06:36.680 --> 06:38.040
The current statements

06:39.390 --> 06:41.310
all lack substantial evidence.

06:41.650 --> 06:43.400
All the information comes from

06:43.430 --> 06:46.220
the one-sided stories of
the landlord and neighbors.

06:46.220 --> 06:47.950
So it could only be left at that.

06:48.180 --> 06:49.310
Alright, tomorrow,

06:49.390 --> 06:50.840
I'll go to the branch again

06:50.840 --> 06:52.409
and have them check
the birth certificates.

06:52.409 --> 06:53.409
If they're twins,

06:53.680 --> 06:54.310
the scope

06:54.630 --> 06:55.810
shouldn't be too large.

06:55.810 --> 06:56.940
I already checked.

06:57.640 --> 06:59.700
No one matched the criminal profile.

07:00.270 --> 07:02.060
Do we have the address of
the place that woman rented?

07:02.060 --> 07:02.530
Yes.

07:03.270 --> 07:05.850
Since we can't find information
on the children, let's try the mother.

07:05.850 --> 07:08.240
Is it really necessary
to go find the landlord?

07:08.240 --> 07:09.480
No need to find the landlord.

07:09.480 --> 07:10.410
Let's track down

07:10.430 --> 07:12.290
the pimps operating in that area.

07:16.830 --> 07:18.430
As for this matter you're investigating,

07:18.430 --> 07:20.120
you don't even have a clear target.

07:20.120 --> 07:21.390
It's been 20 to 30 years.

07:21.390 --> 07:23.870
Where do you expect me
to find these people for you?

07:23.870 --> 07:26.000
There must at least be some records of
vice sweeps, right?

07:26.000 --> 07:28.160
We plan to start screening
people with prior criminal records.

07:28.160 --> 07:28.820
Captain Li,

07:28.830 --> 07:29.830
what do you think?

07:30.120 --> 07:32.310
The computer records only go up to 2000.

07:32.310 --> 07:33.510
What you want to check

07:33.750 --> 07:36.280
is way past that time frame,
my dear comrades.

07:36.680 --> 07:38.240
There must be paper records, right?

07:38.240 --> 07:40.640
Hopefully the mice haven't chewed them up.

07:41.240 --> 07:42.000
Li,

07:42.040 --> 07:42.870
we won't hold you up...

07:42.870 --> 07:44.600
Don't try to get chummy with me.

07:44.600 --> 07:45.510
Let me tell you,

07:45.560 --> 07:46.380
you've got no clout

07:46.380 --> 07:47.430
with me!

07:54.950 --> 07:57.630
The two of us really screwed him over
back in the day.

07:57.630 --> 07:58.390
To this day,

07:59.310 --> 08:01.040
he still hasn't been promoted.

08:09.070 --> 08:10.200
Everything's here.

08:12.070 --> 08:12.950
Leaders,

08:13.310 --> 08:14.950
don't blame me for not assisting you.

08:14.950 --> 08:16.000
As you can see,

08:16.120 --> 08:17.390
I'm short on manpower here.

08:17.390 --> 08:19.000
I hope you can understand.

08:19.360 --> 08:21.070
I'll leave Xu with you.

08:21.630 --> 08:22.740
He'll dig through all this with you guys

08:22.740 --> 08:25.070
like searching for a needle in a haystack.

08:25.120 --> 08:26.680
If you can find anything this way,

08:26.680 --> 08:28.340
I'll admit you've got skills.

08:28.560 --> 08:29.530
I've got other cases to work on.

08:29.530 --> 08:30.130
Pardon me.

08:36.630 --> 08:37.720
Li is right.

08:38.070 --> 08:39.760
This is no easy task.

08:58.270 --> 08:59.040
How about this?

08:59.040 --> 08:59.960
Let's split up.

09:00.320 --> 09:01.630
I'm familiar with
the vice sweep side of things.

09:01.630 --> 09:02.940
I'll go out on the streets
and feel things out.

09:02.940 --> 09:04.510
You guys keep sifting through
the files here—

09:04.510 --> 09:06.390
focus on checking what

09:06.390 --> 09:07.670
those with prior records are doing now.

09:07.670 --> 09:08.840
Pull out the ones

09:08.840 --> 09:10.200
who've been hanging around the same area

09:10.200 --> 09:11.200
for 20 to 30 years.

09:12.240 --> 09:13.840
Maybe we'll find some clues.

09:15.360 --> 09:17.720
Zhou's idea is not bad.

09:18.400 --> 09:19.600
I'll go with you then.

09:20.080 --> 09:21.120
I'm okay on my own.

09:21.320 --> 09:22.380
I can cover for you.

09:32.470 --> 09:33.700
Take him. Take him.

09:34.000 --> 09:34.530
Go ahead.

09:34.840 --> 09:35.640
I've got this.

09:35.920 --> 09:36.550
Alright.

09:37.240 --> 09:37.790
Let's go.

09:39.800 --> 09:41.360
Mr. Wang, we'll head out first.

09:41.360 --> 09:42.000
Okay.

10:01.620 --> 10:02.550
I'll take the left.

10:02.550 --> 10:03.360
You take the right.

10:03.360 --> 10:04.600
Let's meet at the intersection later.

10:04.600 --> 10:05.080
Okay.

10:06.120 --> 10:06.980
Hey, handsome.

10:07.640 --> 10:09.570
Buy a balloon for your girlfriend.

10:10.630 --> 10:11.960
We're already married.

10:12.390 --> 10:14.110
Then buy it for your kid.

10:19.420 --> 10:21.880
I'll wait for you
at the intersection ahead.

10:22.440 --> 10:23.040
Handsome.

10:23.190 --> 10:24.070
Buy one.

10:24.270 --> 10:26.200
Both boys and girls love it.

10:26.570 --> 10:27.440
Check out this doggy.

10:27.440 --> 10:28.680
Isn't it pretty?

10:49.040 --> 10:50.440
Hansheng, where are you?

11:05.290 --> 11:06.680
The doggy's so cute.

11:06.700 --> 11:07.620
Is it for me?

11:09.470 --> 11:11.600
Let's go upstairs and chat for a while.

11:11.950 --> 11:12.790
Come on.

11:13.550 --> 11:14.390
It's fine.

11:14.730 --> 11:16.390
Where are you from, handsome?

11:17.640 --> 11:18.670
He already rejected you,

11:18.670 --> 11:19.460
Miss.

11:19.580 --> 11:20.460
Who are you?

11:20.480 --> 11:21.520
Why did you grab me?

11:21.520 --> 11:23.180
I hate it most when other women

11:23.680 --> 11:25.070
get handsy with him.

11:27.610 --> 11:28.610
What's your name?

11:30.790 --> 11:32.030
Entrapment, huh?

11:32.360 --> 11:34.030
You guys really went all out.

11:34.310 --> 11:35.700
Just answer the questions.

11:35.700 --> 11:37.360
Or do you want me to take you in?

11:39.400 --> 11:40.040
Name.

11:40.330 --> 11:40.970
Feifei.

11:41.120 --> 11:41.790
Real name.

11:43.320 --> 11:44.120
Feifei...

11:44.140 --> 11:44.900
Li.

11:46.370 --> 11:47.170
What do you do?

11:47.600 --> 11:49.930
You caught me,
and you're asking what I do?

11:50.200 --> 11:52.210
I should be asking you that question.

11:52.210 --> 11:53.090
Be serious.

11:55.360 --> 11:56.960
We want to ask you something.

11:58.510 --> 12:00.030
So you're not the vice squad?

12:00.030 --> 12:01.320
I knew it.

12:01.960 --> 12:03.890
I recognize the cops around here.

12:04.200 --> 12:06.510
I've never seen a woman in the vice squad.

12:07.510 --> 12:08.360
I want to know—

12:09.060 --> 12:10.260
who manages you guys?

12:10.470 --> 12:11.570
Why should I tell you?

12:11.570 --> 12:12.610
So someone does.

12:12.640 --> 12:13.900
I was just saying that.

12:18.720 --> 12:19.320
Hansheng.

12:23.550 --> 12:24.240
Spit it out.

12:25.750 --> 12:26.550
Well,

12:26.750 --> 12:28.790
I usually find my clients myself,

12:29.200 --> 12:30.250
but some

12:30.440 --> 12:32.040
are referred to me by others.

12:32.180 --> 12:33.150
800 a client,

12:33.170 --> 12:34.430
and they take a 300 cut.

12:34.670 --> 12:35.760
So who assigns you the work?

12:35.760 --> 12:36.550
Hong.

12:37.240 --> 12:38.030
Hong?

12:38.240 --> 12:39.440
What's his full name?

12:39.480 --> 12:41.080
I just know him as Hong.

12:41.300 --> 12:42.290
It's not like we're students at school—

12:42.290 --> 12:43.600
who uses full names?

12:44.750 --> 12:46.950
How long has he been in this line of work?

12:47.330 --> 12:49.390
He's always been doing this, I think.

12:49.400 --> 12:50.730
Longer than me, anyway.

13:08.390 --> 13:09.120
Is this him?

13:09.150 --> 13:10.200
Named Hong Cheng.

13:13.600 --> 13:15.260
Bring him in for questioning.

13:15.680 --> 13:16.470
Well...

13:17.440 --> 13:18.720
What's so hard about that?

13:18.720 --> 13:22.320
It's not like we're searching for a needle
in a haystack anymore.

13:26.120 --> 13:27.000
Li?

13:27.510 --> 13:28.390
Li!

13:42.720 --> 13:43.600
Um,

13:44.120 --> 13:44.910
Wang.

13:45.710 --> 13:47.370
Officer Zhou, Officer Jiang.

13:47.760 --> 13:48.800
Hong Cheng

13:48.850 --> 13:49.510
confessed.

13:50.410 --> 13:52.340
Over 20 years ago, that area

13:52.420 --> 13:53.980
was run by one of his senior guys,

13:53.980 --> 13:55.340
named Yu Liang,

13:55.390 --> 13:57.070
who was involved in this line of work.

13:57.070 --> 13:58.110
That Yu Liang

13:58.130 --> 13:59.390
did time for a few years

13:59.520 --> 14:00.610
and is out now.

14:01.850 --> 14:03.380
Did you ask about the twins?

14:03.480 --> 14:04.080
I did.

14:04.550 --> 14:05.680
This is the key part.

14:06.420 --> 14:07.610
Hong Cheng

14:07.640 --> 14:09.000
once heard Yu Liang brag

14:09.440 --> 14:11.630
that when he was young,

14:11.740 --> 14:13.740
he dated a woman

14:13.770 --> 14:15.030
who was raising twins.

14:16.220 --> 14:17.860
Do we have Yu Liang's address?

14:17.860 --> 14:18.980
Yes, it's here.

14:21.710 --> 14:23.510
I printed out a copy of
all the information

14:23.510 --> 14:24.640
I could find for you.

14:25.940 --> 14:26.730
Thank you.

14:29.570 --> 14:30.380
Li.

14:32.940 --> 14:35.260
So I've still got some clout
with you, right?

14:35.260 --> 14:36.420
What do you mean you've got clout?

14:36.420 --> 14:39.550
I'm doing this out of respect
for Officer Zhou, alright?

14:42.660 --> 14:44.140
Li. Li!

14:48.070 --> 14:49.950
I know who you are looking for.

14:51.420 --> 14:52.180
It's Qi Zhen.

14:53.420 --> 14:55.140
Back when I first met Qi Zhen,

14:55.690 --> 14:56.890
she came to Huaiguang

14:57.380 --> 14:58.240
to make a living

14:59.180 --> 15:00.580
and stepped onto my turf.

15:01.240 --> 15:02.500
As soon as she arrived,

15:03.310 --> 15:04.870
the girls working under me

15:05.660 --> 15:07.190
couldn't get any business.

15:07.660 --> 15:08.510
So,

15:09.010 --> 15:11.010
I went to her place to cause trouble.

15:11.210 --> 15:12.290
The moment I saw her,

15:12.290 --> 15:13.120
I understood.

15:14.730 --> 15:16.130
Zhen was very beautiful,

15:17.810 --> 15:18.740
the kind of woman

15:19.610 --> 15:21.270
any man would be captivated by

15:21.420 --> 15:22.570
at first sight.

15:24.420 --> 15:25.060
Later,

15:26.300 --> 15:28.500
I went to cause trouble a few more times.

15:29.610 --> 15:31.300
Unexpectedly, we ended up

15:31.970 --> 15:33.920
becoming familiar with each other.

15:33.920 --> 15:35.050
I only found out then

15:35.300 --> 15:36.560
that she wasn't alone—

15:37.780 --> 15:38.910
she was with a child,

15:40.900 --> 15:41.780
her own child.

15:43.210 --> 15:44.810
They were originally twins,

15:45.380 --> 15:47.020
but the older brother had died,

15:47.020 --> 15:48.950
leaving just the younger brother.

15:49.940 --> 15:51.400
What was the child's name?

15:53.140 --> 15:53.970
I don't know

15:54.970 --> 15:55.780
his full name.

15:57.380 --> 15:58.610
His nickname was

16:00.180 --> 16:01.140
either An...

16:02.570 --> 16:03.970
Or Yan.

16:04.530 --> 16:06.310
Zhen was very sensitive about people

16:06.310 --> 16:07.640
asking about her child,

16:07.720 --> 16:08.850
so I didn't ask much.

16:09.450 --> 16:10.710
Why was she sensitive?

16:11.260 --> 16:12.120
She was worried

16:13.060 --> 16:14.970
that the child would be taken away.

16:14.970 --> 16:15.850
I remember

16:16.540 --> 16:17.540
one night,

16:18.090 --> 16:19.020
it was raining,

16:19.180 --> 16:21.330
she came banging on my door in a panic,

16:21.690 --> 16:23.620
saying the child had gone missing.

16:23.880 --> 16:25.060
Seeing her so anxious,

16:25.060 --> 16:26.220
I picked up the phone

16:26.310 --> 16:27.370
to call the police.

16:27.900 --> 16:29.180
To my surprise, she suddenly snatched

16:29.180 --> 16:30.380
the phone from me,

16:30.380 --> 16:31.710
refusing to let me do it.

16:32.570 --> 16:33.540
Well, Zhen had

16:34.060 --> 16:35.420
lost a son

16:35.730 --> 16:37.190
and had been traumatized.

16:37.380 --> 16:38.020
You know,

16:38.690 --> 16:40.350
she was a bit neurotic up here.

16:41.260 --> 16:42.290
She always felt someone

16:42.290 --> 16:44.350
was going to take this child away too.

16:44.380 --> 16:45.450
Later, I

16:45.450 --> 16:47.060
found the child

16:47.540 --> 16:48.570
in her closet.

16:49.690 --> 16:50.350
In a closet?

16:50.490 --> 16:51.020
Yeah.

16:51.730 --> 16:53.020
Right... In a closet.

16:54.690 --> 16:55.660
So this child—

16:56.660 --> 16:58.850
how old was he then? Was he in school?

16:59.610 --> 17:00.420
At the time,

17:00.810 --> 17:02.610
I think he was about 10 years old.

17:03.300 --> 17:04.560
He didn't go to school.

17:04.770 --> 17:06.099
Zhen wouldn't allow it,

17:06.420 --> 17:07.730
and she wouldn't let him go outside
either.

17:07.730 --> 17:09.660
They just stayed at home every day.

17:09.750 --> 17:11.220
She said she'd teach him herself.

17:10.020 --> 17:17.880
[1989]

17:12.730 --> 17:13.619
Sometimes,

17:14.050 --> 17:14.970
when Zhen

17:15.540 --> 17:16.780
was sewing clothes

17:17.530 --> 17:18.940
or doing handicrafts,

17:19.420 --> 17:21.050
the kid would watch her.

17:21.619 --> 17:23.220
Zhen liked to play the piano,

17:24.010 --> 17:25.869
and the kid liked to listen to her.

17:27.140 --> 17:27.819
I think

17:28.620 --> 17:30.900
that must have been
the biggest entertainment

17:30.900 --> 17:32.160
for the mother and son.

17:32.670 --> 17:33.260
Is it pretty?

17:33.260 --> 17:33.940
Yes.

17:34.600 --> 17:37.330
The mother and son
had a very close relationship.

17:38.190 --> 17:39.040
That kid

17:40.290 --> 17:41.180
was hardly

17:42.380 --> 17:44.380
ever out of Zhen's sight.

17:46.290 --> 17:47.140
Even...

17:52.190 --> 17:53.040
Even when

17:53.420 --> 17:55.480
someone came to their house to visit,

17:55.590 --> 17:56.790
she would find a place

17:57.210 --> 17:58.970
to hide that kid.

18:24.660 --> 18:26.460
You're in quite a good mood, huh?

18:28.870 --> 18:29.940
I like the dark.

18:35.800 --> 18:36.530
Jiang Cheng.

18:38.620 --> 18:40.340
Do you know what it feels like
to be locked

18:40.340 --> 18:41.870
in a dark, enclosed closet?

18:44.730 --> 18:45.820
Suffocated?

18:46.140 --> 18:46.900
Scared?

19:02.570 --> 19:03.680
I like the night.

19:04.990 --> 19:06.250
It makes you feel safe—

19:08.180 --> 19:09.830
like an owl in the darkness.

19:11.830 --> 19:13.140
Only you can see

19:14.050 --> 19:14.860
and hear.

19:16.100 --> 19:18.700
The whole world seems to be
under your control.

19:19.730 --> 19:20.490
Yet

19:22.020 --> 19:24.370
no one even knows you exist.

19:45.660 --> 19:46.720
Please take a look.

19:46.730 --> 19:47.660
Is this Qi Yan?

19:48.720 --> 19:50.720
T-This is too blurry.

19:51.100 --> 19:51.770
Besides,

19:52.290 --> 19:53.750
he was just a kid back then.

19:54.970 --> 19:55.940
I can't tell.

19:58.900 --> 20:00.900
Then do you know where Qi Zhen is now?

20:02.450 --> 20:02.940
I...

20:03.290 --> 20:04.860
I thought you knew.

20:06.490 --> 20:07.490
The mother and son

20:07.690 --> 20:09.550
have been missing for many years.

20:11.450 --> 20:12.420
Do you remember

20:12.490 --> 20:13.940
where you saw her

20:14.140 --> 20:15.140
for the last time?

20:16.100 --> 20:17.050
I can't remember

20:18.380 --> 20:19.510
when it was clearly.

20:19.690 --> 20:20.940
I think

20:22.820 --> 20:24.050
it was in 1992.

20:24.730 --> 20:26.820
But I remember the place very clearly.

20:26.820 --> 20:28.480
It was in Huaiguang Hospital.

20:28.580 --> 20:29.380
She was sent to the hospital

20:29.380 --> 20:30.050
because

20:30.770 --> 20:32.370
she tried to commit suicide.

20:33.380 --> 20:34.710
By slitting her wrists?

20:36.210 --> 20:36.820
Yes.

20:38.250 --> 20:38.730
I

20:39.690 --> 20:41.420
went to the hospital to see her.

20:41.620 --> 20:42.950
She was lying in the bed,

20:44.470 --> 20:45.730
her face deathly pale.

20:46.610 --> 20:48.270
I tried to talk sense into her.

20:48.420 --> 20:49.180
I said,

20:50.530 --> 20:52.010
"Even if you won't think for yourself,

20:52.010 --> 20:53.280
you have to think for your kid.

20:53.280 --> 20:55.210
What will happen to him if you die?"

20:55.940 --> 20:56.590
She

20:56.900 --> 20:58.010
didn't say a word.

20:58.900 --> 21:00.030
Just lying there.

21:01.660 --> 21:02.660
There was no light

21:03.250 --> 21:04.380
in her eyes at all,

21:04.830 --> 21:06.070
like a living dead.

21:08.180 --> 21:09.710
Fortunately, at that time,

21:09.950 --> 21:11.240
the police officers

21:11.580 --> 21:12.560
were going door to door

21:12.560 --> 21:14.920
conducting a household survey.

21:15.770 --> 21:16.530
Otherwise,

21:17.420 --> 21:18.550
she would have died.

21:19.730 --> 21:20.420
Later,

21:21.180 --> 21:23.040
when I went to the hospital again,

21:24.690 --> 21:25.730
Zhen was gone.

21:26.530 --> 21:28.260
I asked the doctors and nurses.

21:28.730 --> 21:29.530
They said

21:29.560 --> 21:31.160
she sneaked away by herself,

21:31.860 --> 21:33.860
and they didn't know where she went.

21:37.580 --> 21:38.640
From that point on,

21:39.900 --> 21:41.700
she just vanished into thin air.

21:43.490 --> 21:43.970
I...

21:45.730 --> 21:46.690
But I always feel

21:47.820 --> 21:48.820
she's not dead—

21:50.050 --> 21:51.380
that she's still alive.

21:52.140 --> 21:52.820
Maybe

21:53.770 --> 21:55.340
she didn't go far at all.

21:55.580 --> 21:57.640
Maybe she's right here in Huaiguang.

21:57.900 --> 21:58.760
Over the years,

21:58.900 --> 21:59.660
I think

22:00.530 --> 22:01.930
I've seen her a few times.

22:02.770 --> 22:04.030
Once, from a distance,

22:05.340 --> 22:06.450
I saw her right at the alley entrance.

22:06.450 --> 22:07.510
But when I ran over,

22:09.210 --> 22:09.940
she was gone.

22:11.100 --> 22:12.450
Once on the street,

22:12.450 --> 22:14.620
it felt like we brushed past each other.

22:14.620 --> 22:16.020
But when I turned my head,

22:17.430 --> 22:18.430
she disappeared.

22:19.490 --> 22:21.050
I can't tell if it was

22:21.050 --> 22:23.340
my hallucination or if I really saw her.

22:23.770 --> 22:24.380
You see,

22:24.450 --> 22:25.250
a woman—

22:25.530 --> 22:26.380
for her child—

22:26.440 --> 22:29.050
was willing to do anything
and had done everything.

22:29.050 --> 22:30.770
She already knew no limit.

22:31.560 --> 22:32.160
But why...

22:32.900 --> 22:34.560
Why would she commit suicide?

22:34.940 --> 22:37.940
What would happen to the child
if she really died? I...

22:40.250 --> 22:41.650
I just don't understand.

22:42.490 --> 22:43.720
In your memory,

22:44.340 --> 22:46.200
did Qi Zhen ever wear red clothes?

22:46.380 --> 22:46.900
Yes.

22:49.730 --> 22:50.770
She liked red.

22:51.870 --> 22:52.730
She made most of

22:52.860 --> 22:54.260
her own dresses herself.

22:55.940 --> 22:57.400
They were very beautiful.

23:00.740 --> 23:04.310
Qi Zhen attempted suicide
by slitting her wrists when she was young.

23:04.310 --> 23:05.700
In all of our cases,

23:06.350 --> 23:08.550
the fatal wounds on the victims' wrists

23:08.800 --> 23:10.930
are a consistent criminal signature.

23:11.940 --> 23:12.580
Chief Tan.

23:13.240 --> 23:15.060
During the process of
committing the crimes, Qi Yan

23:15.060 --> 23:16.440
kept setting up

23:16.470 --> 23:18.460
scenes filled with ritualistic elements.

23:18.460 --> 23:19.730
It should be a projection of the scene

23:19.730 --> 23:21.430
when his mother slit her wrists
to commit suicide.

23:21.430 --> 23:22.830
By recreating the scene,

23:22.860 --> 23:24.860
he repeatedly brings himself back to
that moment,

23:24.860 --> 23:25.660
seeking

23:25.920 --> 23:27.190
some kind of psychological

23:27.190 --> 23:28.560
comfort and relief.

23:29.620 --> 23:30.890
But I still haven't figured out

23:30.890 --> 23:31.820
why he does this.

23:32.900 --> 23:34.100
Generally speaking,

23:34.180 --> 23:35.230
painful memories

23:35.410 --> 23:37.360
aren't something people deliberately
try to repeat,

23:37.360 --> 23:39.490
and killing isn't meant to be
a form of self-torture.

23:39.490 --> 23:41.640
The reason that drove Qi Zhen
to attempt suicide,

23:41.640 --> 23:42.470
and the reason Qi Yan

23:42.470 --> 23:44.470
kept recreating the suicide scene—

23:44.620 --> 23:46.610
if we can figure out these two things,

23:46.610 --> 23:47.940
then psychologically,

23:48.200 --> 23:51.000
we can completely get a handle on
Qi Yan as a person.

23:51.060 --> 23:52.590
I understand what you mean.

23:53.800 --> 23:54.480
Mentor.

23:54.730 --> 23:56.570
We want to go meet

23:56.600 --> 23:58.730
the police officer
who helped Qi Zhen back then.

23:58.730 --> 23:59.530
Sure.

24:00.010 --> 24:02.540
Just go straight to
the local police station.

24:02.580 --> 24:04.420
There shouldn't be many people
in charge of household registration.

24:04.420 --> 24:05.980
He should be easy enough to find.

24:05.980 --> 24:07.510
Well, you may not know this,

24:07.970 --> 24:09.380
but our Professor Jiang

24:10.180 --> 24:12.510
isn't exactly welcome here in Huaiguang.

24:12.580 --> 24:15.180
We've already run into
quite a few roadblocks.

24:17.210 --> 24:18.210
I didn't expect

24:18.270 --> 24:20.530
Professor Jiang to have times
when things don't go his way.

24:20.530 --> 24:21.140
It's fine.

24:21.210 --> 24:22.370
I'll talk to them.

24:22.820 --> 24:24.450
We'll just send an official letter,

24:24.450 --> 24:25.010
alright?

24:25.690 --> 24:28.040
Now that we finally have
conclusive evidence,

24:28.040 --> 24:29.580
no one will dare to delay the case.

24:29.580 --> 24:30.140
Okay.

24:30.900 --> 24:31.970
Anything else?

24:35.100 --> 24:35.860
Mentor,

24:35.970 --> 24:38.320
there's nothing else.

24:38.660 --> 24:39.290
Okay then.

24:41.690 --> 24:43.090
Finding out about Qi Zhen

24:43.140 --> 24:44.200
was not easy at all.

24:44.530 --> 24:45.990
Thanks for your hard work.

24:46.100 --> 24:47.700
Alright. Please rest early.

24:47.790 --> 24:49.380
Alright. Bye.

24:51.180 --> 24:51.730
Gosh.

24:51.730 --> 24:53.440
My mentor is way too talkative.

24:53.440 --> 24:54.580
We talked for over half an hour.

24:54.580 --> 24:55.910
Get me a bottle of water.

25:06.450 --> 25:07.450
You smell so good.

25:07.820 --> 25:09.280
It's a floral scent today.

25:09.730 --> 25:11.990
I'm the National Little Rose, after all.

25:13.380 --> 25:14.230
Professor Jiang,

25:14.230 --> 25:15.690
so you know how to joke now.

25:16.140 --> 25:17.020
I always have.

25:20.100 --> 25:21.180
He's lying.

25:26.430 --> 25:27.080
Zhou Jin,

25:28.690 --> 25:30.290
I thought you booked one room

25:30.820 --> 25:32.620
because you wanted to be with me.

25:34.690 --> 25:36.010
I am with you.

25:39.290 --> 25:40.010
Are you?

25:52.900 --> 25:53.760
Let's go to bed.

26:10.070 --> 26:11.350
I didn't mean to.

26:12.780 --> 26:14.050
There were really no other rooms left—

26:14.050 --> 26:15.510
only a standard twin room.

26:16.340 --> 26:17.140
Besides,

26:17.860 --> 26:19.190
you are a light sleeper.

26:20.070 --> 26:22.130
I want you to sleep more comfortably.

26:23.730 --> 26:25.660
How do you know I'm a light sleeper?

26:28.410 --> 26:30.730
When two people have been together
for a long time,

26:30.730 --> 26:32.930
they know everything about each other.

26:46.860 --> 26:48.210
Why do you think Yu Liang

26:52.650 --> 26:54.930
cares so much about Qi Zhen?

26:56.420 --> 26:58.220
He's waited for her for 20 years.

26:58.790 --> 27:01.320
It can't just be because
she's pretty, right?

27:04.560 --> 27:06.890
I guess everyone has their own obsession.

27:09.080 --> 27:11.000
But I could tell

27:12.470 --> 27:14.270
that he's truly waiting for her.

27:14.450 --> 27:16.310
He could even wait for a lifetime.

27:18.410 --> 27:19.600
If it were you,

27:20.200 --> 27:21.930
would you be willing to do that?

27:24.630 --> 27:25.520
I have waited.

27:27.830 --> 27:29.440
Then I understood a saying,

27:34.160 --> 27:35.490
"People who can bravely

27:37.130 --> 27:38.450
say goodbye

27:40.400 --> 27:42.600
will be rewarded with a new beginning."

27:52.180 --> 27:53.640
Turn off the light, Hubby.

28:04.250 --> 28:05.650
What did you just call me?

28:08.380 --> 28:08.940
Hubby.

28:23.820 --> 28:24.750
Jiang Hansheng,

28:26.970 --> 28:28.420
you're a good husband.

28:33.660 --> 28:34.380
Zhou Jin.

28:36.510 --> 28:38.240
When we have kids in the future,

28:38.690 --> 28:40.090
what should we name them?

28:43.180 --> 28:45.250
I think I will be a qualified father.

29:22.850 --> 29:26.370
[Yatou Pharmaceutical Factory]

29:31.340 --> 29:32.000
We're here.

29:32.900 --> 29:34.340
Untie our new friend.

29:36.870 --> 29:37.400
Hands.

29:48.070 --> 29:49.070
Get out of the car.

30:03.290 --> 30:04.160
Where is this?

30:10.790 --> 30:12.390
Are you going to kill me here?

30:15.930 --> 30:16.730
Old Scorpion,

30:17.460 --> 30:18.920
you didn't keep your word.

30:31.130 --> 30:33.460
You did a good job with
what I told you to do.

30:33.740 --> 30:34.370
Qiu Ye,

30:34.520 --> 30:36.050
Boss He, and Qi

30:36.870 --> 30:38.470
all strongly recommend you.

30:39.170 --> 30:41.230
Looks like I should give you a chance.

30:42.260 --> 30:43.170
Qi?

30:44.580 --> 30:45.380
That's right.

30:45.600 --> 30:46.490
Qi.

30:49.860 --> 30:50.990
Who exactly are you?

30:53.760 --> 30:54.490
Jiang Cheng,

30:55.770 --> 30:57.100
welcome on board.

31:00.940 --> 31:02.100
I am Old Scorpion.

31:08.410 --> 31:09.010
By the way,

31:10.720 --> 31:12.580
your marksmanship is just so-so.

31:12.740 --> 31:14.670
I'll give you some guidance later.

31:19.660 --> 31:20.230
Let's go.

31:32.210 --> 31:32.770
Zhou Jin,

31:33.120 --> 31:34.580
I will send you some files,

31:34.610 --> 31:36.180
including the police dispatch records

31:36.180 --> 31:36.660
and

31:37.050 --> 31:38.450
the contact information
of the police officer

31:38.450 --> 31:40.100
who saved Qi Zhen back then.

31:40.380 --> 31:42.240
The officer is called Jian Liang.

31:42.240 --> 31:43.060
Over 20 years ago,

31:43.060 --> 31:45.340
he was a household registration officer
in the Xiacheng District of Huaiguang.

31:45.340 --> 31:46.890
Later, he was transferred to
Huiping County

31:46.890 --> 31:51.930
[Huiping, Jingzhou]

31:47.100 --> 31:49.200
and became the head of the police station.

31:49.200 --> 31:51.400
Huiping isn't far. You can drive there.

31:51.410 --> 31:52.530
It only takes an hour.

31:52.530 --> 31:54.060
He will cooperate with you.

31:56.480 --> 31:57.670
Is this Chief Jian?

31:57.900 --> 31:58.820
I am Zhou Jin

31:58.970 --> 32:00.730
from the Nancheng Branch of Haizhou City.

32:00.730 --> 32:01.420
Hello.

32:02.530 --> 32:03.860
What case is it exactly?

32:06.620 --> 32:08.660
We'd like to talk to you in person.

32:09.210 --> 32:09.900
Chief Jian,

32:09.900 --> 32:10.860
how about we meet directly

32:10.860 --> 32:12.210
at the police station?

32:13.620 --> 32:15.070
I got an emergency call,

32:15.090 --> 32:16.490
so I'm outside right now.

32:17.010 --> 32:17.660
Then how about

32:17.660 --> 32:19.660
we just wait for you at the station?

32:22.240 --> 32:23.110
I'm sorry,

32:23.380 --> 32:25.760
but my wife
hasn't been feeling well recently,

32:25.760 --> 32:27.430
so I have to go home in a bit.

32:29.740 --> 32:30.380
How about this?

32:30.380 --> 32:31.820
If you two don't mind,

32:32.170 --> 32:33.320
we can talk at my place.

32:33.320 --> 32:34.320
What do you think?

32:34.640 --> 32:36.440
That doesn't seem appropriate.

32:36.540 --> 32:37.780
It's fine.

32:37.950 --> 32:38.840
I'm the host,

32:38.970 --> 32:40.680
so it's only right to treat you to a meal.

32:40.680 --> 32:41.720
Not to brag,

32:41.970 --> 32:43.880
but my wife is a really good cook.

32:43.910 --> 32:44.520
I mean it.

32:45.690 --> 32:46.750
Then it's settled.

32:46.800 --> 32:47.500
I'll send the address

32:47.500 --> 32:48.960
to your phone number later.

32:48.960 --> 32:49.640
Alright?

32:55.820 --> 32:57.020
Let's go to his house.

33:00.340 --> 33:01.060
602.

33:01.340 --> 33:02.600
This should be the one.

33:04.800 --> 33:05.430
Coming.

33:11.360 --> 33:12.040
Hello.

33:12.260 --> 33:13.970
We are here for Chief Jian.

33:15.580 --> 33:16.410
Officer Zhou.

33:17.930 --> 33:18.930
Professor Jiang.

33:20.370 --> 33:21.210
Come on.

33:21.240 --> 33:22.240
Please come on in.

33:23.730 --> 33:24.380
Come in.

33:24.670 --> 33:26.670
I've got the slippers ready for you.

33:29.200 --> 33:31.780
Something came up,
and Jian hasn't returned yet.

33:31.780 --> 33:32.490
Please, have a seat.

33:32.490 --> 33:34.050
I'll go make some tea for you.

33:34.050 --> 33:35.850
Please don't trouble yourself.

33:36.100 --> 33:37.290
I'm his wife.

33:37.430 --> 33:38.430
You are so young.

33:38.540 --> 33:39.690
Just call me ma'am.

33:40.590 --> 33:41.310
Come on in.

33:41.340 --> 33:42.740
Make yourselves at home.

33:44.070 --> 33:45.800
Please, come in and have a seat.

34:17.440 --> 34:18.560
Funny, right?

34:19.030 --> 34:19.820
Who would hang their police uniform

34:19.820 --> 34:21.489
on the wall in their own home?

34:21.670 --> 34:23.330
Like some kind of narcissist.

34:23.610 --> 34:24.300
Not at all.

34:25.130 --> 34:27.090
Since his first day as a police officer,

34:27.090 --> 34:28.420
Jian has had this habit.

34:28.690 --> 34:29.830
Every morning when he wakes up,

34:29.830 --> 34:30.900
he has to look at it

34:31.219 --> 34:32.219
to remind himself

34:32.370 --> 34:34.770
to be loyal to his duty
and work diligently.

34:35.610 --> 34:36.570
He also says

34:36.600 --> 34:38.739
it's not safe for me to be
alone at home so often.

34:38.739 --> 34:40.500
By hanging a police uniform here,

34:40.500 --> 34:41.830
even if a thief broke in,

34:41.909 --> 34:43.170
they wouldn't dare steal anything.

34:43.170 --> 34:44.780
He's just that kind of person.

34:44.780 --> 34:46.900
Please excuse him.

34:48.130 --> 34:49.260
Here, have some tea.

34:51.360 --> 34:51.960
By the way,

34:52.530 --> 34:54.219
what do you want to eat for lunch today?

34:54.219 --> 34:55.090
Tell me,

34:55.120 --> 34:56.449
and I'll make it for you.

34:57.930 --> 34:58.970
We are not picky.

35:00.530 --> 35:01.590
Just not too spicy.

35:02.740 --> 35:04.170
I can help you.

35:04.820 --> 35:05.450
Sure.

35:05.690 --> 35:07.490
See if the dishes I prepared

35:07.610 --> 35:08.740
suit your taste.

35:09.170 --> 35:10.450
We don't often have young people over,

35:10.450 --> 35:12.050
so I don't know what you like.

35:13.570 --> 35:15.050
Have some fruit first.

35:16.920 --> 35:17.520
Let's go.

35:18.800 --> 35:20.400
Make yourself comfortable.

35:32.780 --> 35:33.970
Jian told me

35:34.900 --> 35:37.830
that you guys are from
the CIB of Haizhou City, right?

35:40.780 --> 35:42.510
Being a criminal investigator

35:42.980 --> 35:44.110
must be tiring, huh?

35:44.860 --> 35:45.570
It's alright.

35:45.570 --> 35:47.470
It's just there have been
quite a few cases lately.

35:47.470 --> 35:48.730
Jian is also like this,

35:49.260 --> 35:51.320
busy all day without a moment to rest.

35:52.750 --> 35:53.830
That's what it's like

35:53.830 --> 35:55.090
to be a police officer—

35:55.760 --> 35:57.890
working tirelessly around the clock.

36:03.050 --> 36:03.690
By the way,

36:04.900 --> 36:06.360
what case brought you guys

36:06.570 --> 36:07.820
all the way here?

36:12.150 --> 36:14.660
It can't be that
Jian got into some trouble, right?

36:14.660 --> 36:15.610
No, it's not.

37:26.720 --> 37:28.890
The perpetrator may not necessarily have
a deficiency in romantic relationships.

37:28.890 --> 37:30.820
Rather, the issue lies in the mother-child
relationship from his early years.

37:30.820 --> 37:32.120
He grew up in a single-parent household,

37:32.120 --> 37:33.720
raised solely by his mother,

37:34.430 --> 37:37.040
and he developed very serious
psychological problems.

37:37.040 --> 37:38.180
It's also highly likely that

37:38.180 --> 37:39.490
he experienced betrayal,

37:39.490 --> 37:41.550
abandonment, or abuse by his mother,

37:41.700 --> 37:43.190
which led to a distorted personality.

37:43.190 --> 37:44.660
While obsessed with women,

37:44.660 --> 37:47.060
he also harbors extreme hatred
toward them.

37:47.060 --> 37:47.940
When Zhen

37:48.360 --> 37:49.420
was making clothes

37:49.640 --> 37:50.970
and doing handicrafts,

37:52.280 --> 37:53.910
that child would watch her.

37:54.650 --> 37:56.250
Zhen liked to play the piano,

37:56.470 --> 37:57.940
and the child liked to listen to it.

37:57.940 --> 37:59.830
The police officer
who saved Qi Zhen back then

37:59.830 --> 38:01.120
was called Jian Liang.

38:01.550 --> 38:03.350
When I went to the hospital again,

38:03.350 --> 38:04.380
Zhen was gone.

38:04.400 --> 38:05.060
This person

38:05.610 --> 38:08.010
harbors extreme hatred toward the police.

38:09.570 --> 38:10.430
Professor Jiang.

38:10.430 --> 38:11.390
But I always feel

38:11.620 --> 38:12.750
that she's not dead—

38:12.970 --> 38:14.300
that she's still alive.

38:19.980 --> 38:20.730
It's okay. It's okay.

38:20.730 --> 38:21.440
I'm sorry.

38:23.010 --> 38:23.610
It's okay.

38:24.240 --> 38:25.840
It's okay. It doesn't hurt much.

38:25.840 --> 38:28.260
I just wanted to bring the soup over here

38:28.700 --> 38:30.650
to free up the stove for cooking.

38:30.680 --> 38:31.540
I didn't expect

38:31.860 --> 38:32.740
it to slip.

38:33.150 --> 38:33.900
I'm sorry.

38:34.380 --> 38:35.300
Do you have ice cubes?

38:35.300 --> 38:35.940
I don't.

38:36.940 --> 38:38.530
Maybe you should go to the hospital.

38:38.530 --> 38:40.930
Please go to the hospital right away,
okay?

38:42.280 --> 38:43.610
I'm really okay, ma'am.

38:44.290 --> 38:45.380
I've been calling you ma'am.

38:45.380 --> 38:46.300
I forgot to ask—

38:46.900 --> 38:48.160
what is your last name?

38:49.430 --> 38:50.710
M-My last name is Xie.

38:53.200 --> 38:54.660
What about your full name?

38:57.670 --> 38:58.550
Get out.

38:58.940 --> 38:59.800
Get out of here.

38:59.950 --> 39:00.950
Calm down, ma'am.

39:00.980 --> 39:02.380
Put the knife down first.

39:03.620 --> 39:04.240
Put the knife down.

39:04.240 --> 39:05.110
Get out of here!

39:05.130 --> 39:06.220
Get out!

39:06.380 --> 39:07.420
Leave my house!

39:08.670 --> 39:10.070
You're not welcome here!

39:10.990 --> 39:12.720
Jian knows nothing about this!

39:12.730 --> 39:13.520
She was

39:13.730 --> 39:14.830
sent to the hospital because

39:14.830 --> 39:16.280
she tried to commit suicide.

39:16.280 --> 39:17.610
By slitting her wrists.

39:18.360 --> 39:19.420
You don't have ice—

39:19.980 --> 39:21.820
do you have anything else frozen?

39:21.820 --> 39:22.680
Please get it for me.

39:22.680 --> 39:23.970
Get out of here, do you hear me?

39:23.970 --> 39:24.740
Get out!

39:24.770 --> 39:25.480
Qi Zhen!

39:26.380 --> 39:28.640
If you want to continue your current life

39:28.710 --> 39:30.980
and don't want to cause trouble
for Chief Jian,

39:30.980 --> 39:32.530
put down the knife in your hand.

39:32.530 --> 39:33.860
Do not try to provoke me.

39:35.300 --> 39:36.780
No. No.

39:37.150 --> 39:38.900
Don't tell him!

39:39.450 --> 39:40.530
No, no, I mean...

39:40.650 --> 39:41.940
I'm not Qi Zhen!

39:42.020 --> 39:43.270
I'm not Qi Zhen!

39:43.290 --> 39:44.350
My name is Xie Meng!

39:44.470 --> 39:45.810
You've got the wrong person!

39:45.810 --> 39:46.810
Please calm down.

39:47.220 --> 39:48.240
Put the knife down first.

39:48.240 --> 39:49.110
Let's talk,

39:49.300 --> 39:49.900
okay?

39:52.160 --> 39:52.990
Why...

39:53.700 --> 39:55.700
Why did you find this place?

39:56.350 --> 39:56.790
You...

39:57.230 --> 39:58.290
You are his people?

39:59.650 --> 40:00.450
Who are you?

40:01.010 --> 40:02.870
You are not police at all, are you?

40:04.420 --> 40:05.480
You are his people.

40:06.450 --> 40:07.900
He sent you to take me

40:08.050 --> 40:09.780
and my son back, didn't he?

40:10.890 --> 40:11.660
Who is he?

40:12.220 --> 40:13.360
Who wants to catch you?

40:13.360 --> 40:14.550
Your son is Qi Yan,

40:14.740 --> 40:15.170
right?

40:15.200 --> 40:15.950
Where is he?

40:18.300 --> 40:19.420
You are too late.

40:20.400 --> 40:21.630
Go back and tell him

40:22.430 --> 40:23.870
that I strangled his son.

40:25.030 --> 40:26.660
His son has long been dead.

40:27.450 --> 40:28.020
I should never have

40:28.020 --> 40:29.530
expected anything good from that child

40:29.530 --> 40:31.060
tainted with filthy blood.

40:31.650 --> 40:33.340
He's a vile creature,

40:33.340 --> 40:35.510
and his son is no better!

40:35.530 --> 40:36.930
They both deserve to die!

40:37.970 --> 40:39.900
You deserve to die too!

40:42.270 --> 40:44.020
Go back and tell him

40:44.750 --> 40:46.610
that I will never go back with you.

40:47.170 --> 40:49.050
And I'm not afraid of him anymore.

40:49.800 --> 40:52.280
Jian Liang is a clean person.

40:52.510 --> 40:54.470
If you dare to lay a finger on him,

40:56.300 --> 40:57.900
I will fight you to the death.

40:58.350 --> 40:59.020
Tell me,

40:59.630 --> 41:00.980
who is Qi Yan's father?

41:03.970 --> 41:05.180
Y-You...

41:05.500 --> 41:06.360
You don't know?

41:08.610 --> 41:10.450
You weren't sent by him?

41:10.700 --> 41:11.380
Qi Zhen.

41:11.530 --> 41:12.820
I am Zhou Jin from
the Criminal Investigation Brigade

41:12.820 --> 41:14.750
of Nancheng Branch, Haizhou City.

41:15.570 --> 41:17.540
There's been a recent case in Haizhou,

41:17.540 --> 41:18.750
and your son, Qi Yan,

41:18.970 --> 41:20.340
is a key suspect.

41:20.380 --> 41:21.170
We actually came today

41:21.170 --> 41:22.490
to talk to Jian Liang

41:22.540 --> 41:23.530
and get your information.

41:23.530 --> 41:24.610
Don't tell me...

41:24.610 --> 41:27.090
Don't tell me anything about him anymore!

41:27.120 --> 41:28.880
Don't bring him up to me again!

41:29.170 --> 41:31.340
Don't bring him up to me again!

41:33.420 --> 41:34.650
But he is your son.

41:34.650 --> 41:35.860
Just because I gave birth to him,

41:35.860 --> 41:37.420
do I have to pay for his sins?

41:40.530 --> 41:41.170
Alright.

41:41.820 --> 41:42.450
Alright.

41:42.940 --> 41:43.940
If I die,

41:44.210 --> 41:46.040
you won't come back, will you?

41:46.770 --> 41:47.850
If I die,

41:48.650 --> 41:50.850
Jian Liang will be left in peace, right?

41:52.280 --> 41:52.940
Alright...

41:55.190 --> 41:55.900
Alright...

41:57.420 --> 41:58.170
Alright...

42:03.530 --> 42:04.170
Hansheng.

42:04.380 --> 42:05.300
I'm sorry.

42:06.490 --> 42:08.140
I'm sorry. I'm sorry.

42:21.940 --> 42:23.170
This lock...

42:23.660 --> 42:25.190
This lock won't open again.

42:27.980 --> 42:28.830
Honey,

42:29.490 --> 42:31.020
this lock won't open again.

42:32.340 --> 42:33.870
Can you open the door for me?

42:34.450 --> 42:35.080
Oh, alright.

42:35.080 --> 42:35.870
It's open.

42:37.580 --> 42:39.470
Honey, this door lock

42:39.490 --> 42:41.020
really needs to be changed.

42:46.960 --> 42:48.560
You arrived even earlier...

42:49.510 --> 42:50.050
Than me.

42:51.760 --> 42:52.720
W-What's wrong?

42:59.130 --> 42:59.860
Are you okay?

43:03.530 --> 43:03.990
This...

43:06.220 --> 43:07.220
What happened?
